### Cancel reservation for an order
POST {{baseUrl}}/inventory/reservations/{{orderId}}/cancel

###

### Confirm reservation for an order
POST {{baseUrl}}/inventory/reservations/{{orderId}}/confirm

###

### Get inventory for a product
GET {{baseUrl}}/inventory/{{productId}}

###

### Get reservation status by orderId
GET {{baseUrl}}/inventory/reservations/{{orderId}}

###

### List all inventory items
GET {{baseUrl}}/inventory

